complaint_info.description: Package not received despite showing as 'delivered' on the Amazon website.

conversation_history.message: Hello! I'm your AI customer service assistant. I'll help you with your issue by asking a few questions. Let's start!
Could you please tell me your name and describe the issue you're experiencing?
I did not get my package but I had to show him delivered on the website of Amazon.
Could you please provide your order number or the tracking number for the package?
Could you please provide your order number or the tracking number associated with the package?
Thank you for providing the information. Let me process what we've discussed.
